    <div class="contentPane">
        <section class="l-page-block l-text-block bottom-line">
            <div class="l-content-container container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <h1>Student life at INTO Manchester</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <p>Welcome to your home from home, the INTO Manchester Centre is a purpose-built learning hub made for you. This is where you'll attend your classes, meet with tutors and where you'll study much of the time. With 39 teaching rooms featuring digital whiteboards, modern computing suites and free Wi-Fi throughout - you'll be sure to have everything you need for a fantastic study experience.</p>
<p>The Learning Resource Centre (LRC) is a learning hot-spot with plenty of resoruces to help you with your course, or if you prefer you can find a comfortable space around the Centre to revise or relax with friends.</p>
<p>The INTO Manchester Centre isn't just about studying though, it's also a place catch up with your new friends. Visit the café to grab a bite to eat or a coffee, or play table football. The Centre's central location in Manchester means you can also visit restaurants or shops nearby for a break.</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
<script type="text/javascript" src="//maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyDLGSVTSKHIwTRMEnl10NY-xcBIzOUgVCM"></script>
<div id="l-map-container"></div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        Into.GoogleMap.displayGoogleMap([{"name":"INTO Manchester campus","lat":53.4751844,"lon":-2.2401488000000427}], "l-map-container");
    });
